[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
That city was a symbol of human despair.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[bg  time="1000"  method="crossfade"  storage="lastwall.jpg"  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
[r]Over a long, long time, despair has taken on a will of its own.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[bg  time="1000"  method="crossfade"  storage="moya120.jpg"  ]
[cm  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
Despair is very lonely, and wants to spend a long, leisurely time enjoying the company of the few remaining humans.[l][r]
He took away everything that was important to Kanazawa,
He casually snapped Ishii's wings. [l][r]
[r]And then he approached Chito and Yuri. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm  ]
[bg  time="1000"  method="crossfade"  storage="lastwall2.jpg"  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
The timid Chito continued to refuse despair, while the kind Yuri played along with despair. [l][r]
[r]I think Despair especially liked these two.[l][r]

[_tb_end_text]

[bg  time="1000"  method="crossfade"  storage="saijousou_non.jpg"  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]

[r]Then, using a glimmer of hope as bait, they lured him to the top floor, and together the three of them tried to fly to the next world. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm  ]
[bg  time="2000"  method="crossfade"  storage="snow.jpg"  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
But Yuri and Chito have become one. [l][r]
[r]Yuri was the only one left, even though he didn't reject her and he didn't want to play with her anymore.[r]
Only Chito left for the next world.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm  ]
[bg  time="1000"  method="crossfade"  storage="moya120.jpg"  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
Despair must have been very anxious. [l][r]
And he waited for a golden opportunity.[l][r]
[r]But that chance was also crushed by Chito and Yuri. [l][r]
Despairing in despair, he spent time with Yuri, who remained behind. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm  ]
[bg  time="1000"  method="crossfade"  storage="moya50.jpg"  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
And I'm sure he was satisfied.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm  ]
[bg  time="2000"  method="crossfade"  storage="black.png"  ]
[bg  time="2500"  method="crossfade"  storage="sky.jpg"  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
The city, now free of despair, no longer needed Yuri,[l][r]
It has allowed me to embark on a journey to the next world.... [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm  ]
[bg  time="2000"  method="crossfade"  storage="camp.jpg"  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
…Of course, this is just a fairy tale. There is no evidence or probability. [l][r]
In the end, we never know the truth, and I doubt whether such a thing even exists.
[l][r]
So we're going to make this the truth for now. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
[r]I'm always open to objections and counterarguments. The wise Tito will reflect them in new truths. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

