[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
[r] "Hey hey," Yu said in a bored tone. [l][r]
"Hey, that was a one-off." [l][r]
"Heyyy," Yu said, smiling as she came next to me. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
And we looked at the sky again
[l]I thought I would never be able to see the starry sky again, just the two of us. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
[r]The air is crystal clear, and the light shines down on us, transcending countless ages. [l][r]
[r]I looked at you. You noticed.
[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

